results.name: Decimal expansion of Toth's constant (or digits of the density of the exponentially squarefree numbers).
link: Vladimir Shevelev, A fast computation of density of exponentially S-numbers, arXiv:1602.04244 [math.NT], 2016.
Laszlo Tóth, On certain arithmetic functions involving exponential divisors, II., Annales Univ. Sci. Budapest., Sect. Comp., 27 (2007), 155-166.
formula: Product_{prime p}(1+Sum_{j>=4}((mu(j)^2 - mu(j-1)^2)/p^j), where mu(n) is the Möbius function.
results.author: _Juan Arias-de-Reyna_, Sep 19 2015
